        </m:semantics>
      </m:math>
    </para>
    <para id="id45428606">i.e., the unit step is a running sum of the unit sample.</para>
    <para id="id45428612">
      <media id="id8336787" alt=""><image src="../../media/graphics4-d6db.png" mime-type="image/png" height="171" width="200"/></media>
    </para>
    <para id="id45428648">The Z-transform of the unit step is</para>
