    <para id="id45298595">8/ Conclusions on relation between DT time functions and pole-zero diagrams</para>
    <para id="id45298603">More rapidly changing exponential time functions, both growing and decaying, have poles that lie further from the point z = 1 in the z-plane.</para>
    <para id="id45298630">Two-minute miniquiz problem</para>
